{
  "texts": [
    "A large section of the young generation has developed effective English skills which have brought better employment and job opportunities to people on a wider scale.",
    "The English language continues to confront challenges on various fronts in different contexts.",
    "It carries certain religious, economic, cultural, and religious overtones.",
    "Some sociocultural and contextual factors affect the attitudes and learning of ESL/EFL learners.",
    "It is an undeniable truth that positive attitudes about a language and its culture have an enormous effect on learners' proficiency and skills."
  ]
}